comments.content: It looks like a **[Caslon Openface](http://web.archive.org/web/20140725141838/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Bitstream&ffam=CaslonOpenface%20BT%20-%20Regular&fid=a90795892f8d7b46b2a51b9b50413129&fsize=60&text=F&fit=1)** or an **[Academy (Engraved)](http://web.archive.org/web/20140725141838/http:/www.findmyfont.com/index.php/fonts/font-preview?fset=Letraset&ffam=Academy%20-%20Engraved&fid=6535d83d1c58352e283a98e0e0639d68&fsize=60&text=F&fit=1)** + the outline deformation.
